# Work Dashboard - Project Overview

Personal work dashboard. React 19 SPA + SSR via TanStack Start, Tailwind v4, Vite 7. Deployed as Node SSR (was Cloudflare Workers via Lovable; migrated to portable Node in May 2026).

## Tech stack
- React 19 + TanStack Router / Start / Query
- Vite 7 + Tailwind CSS 4 (no PostCSS config; `@tailwindcss/vite`)
- TypeScript strict mode, ESLint, Prettier
- shadcn/ui components in `src/lib/ui/`
- Production server: Node 22 + `srvx` (Fetch -> Node adapter)

## Scripts
- `npm run dev` - Vite dev server on http://localhost:5173
- `npm run build` - emits `dist/client/` + `dist/server/server.js`
- `npm run start` - runs `server.mjs` on http://localhost:3000 against the built handler
- `npm run lint` / `npm run format`

## Deployment
- Local: `npm run start` (Node 22.12+)
- Docker: see [`Dockerfile`](Dockerfile) (multi-stage, Node 22 Alpine, HEALTHCHECK on :3000)
- NOT Cloudflare Workers anymore (`wrangler.jsonc` and `@cloudflare/vite-plugin` removed).

## Layout
- `src/routes/` - file-based routes (TanStack Router)
- `src/routes/__root.tsx` - root shell, error/notfound components, head meta
- `src/lib/ui/` - shadcn/ui primitives
- `src/lib/utils.ts` - `cn()` helper
- `src/start.ts` - server middleware (error handling)
- `src/styles.css` - Tailwind v4 theme tokens under `@theme`
- `server.mjs` - production Node entry (do NOT edit unless `dist/server/server.js` path changes)
